---
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
            <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Engineering <span class="text-brand-500">Excellence</span></h2>
            <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-brand-500 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Mastering the entire stack with a focus on architecture, performance, and clean code.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl reveal group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-400/20 to-brand-600/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group text-brand-400 text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-3">AI & Swarm Architecture</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Building state-of-the-art multi-agent swarms and RAG capabilities with Python and Java 21.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl reveal group" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400/20 to-emerald-600/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-server text-emerald-400 text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Low-Latency Systems</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Designing ultra-low-latency zero-copy execution engines for HFT using C++20 and Rust.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl reveal group" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400/20 to-purple-600/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud text-purple-400 text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Web3 & Cloud</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Automating deployments and building intent-centric Smart Accounts with zkML.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
